{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"style","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n<p><strong><code>style</code></strong> 属性指定了指定其元素的样式信息。它的功能与 HTML 中的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/style\">style</a>属性相同。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用环境","title":"使用环境","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Categories</th>\n      <th>Presentation attribute</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Value</td>\n      <td>&lt;style&gt;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Animatable</td>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"style\">&lt;style&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>样式数据的语法取决于样式表语言。默认情况下，如果未指定 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/contentStyleType\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">contentStyleType (en-US)</a></code>，样式表语言为 CSS。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下示例展示了使用 CSS 作为样式表语言来使用 style 属性，为一个矩形框添加样式。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewbox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 1000 500<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>600<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用 style 属性</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#container\">Container elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#filterprimitive\">Filter primitive elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#gradient\">Gradient elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#graphics\">Graphics elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#structural\">Structural elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#textcontent\">Text content elements</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/clipPath\"><code>&lt;clipPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/styling.html#ElementSpecificStyling","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.style.style"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关","title":"相关","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用环境","id":"使用环境"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"}